---
title: Soft Break
---

<ComponentPreview name="soft-break-demo" />

<PackageInfo>

## Features

- Allows insertion of line breaks within a text block without starting a new block

</PackageInfo>

## Usage

```tsx
import { BlockquotePlugin } from '@udecode/plate-blockquote/react';

const plugins = [
  // ...otherPlugins,
  BlockquotePlugin.configure({
    node: {
      isSoftBreak: true,
    },
  }),
];
```
## Keyboard Shortcuts

<KeyTable>
  <KeyTableItem hotkey="Shift + Enter">
    Insert a line break within a block of text without starting a new block
  </KeyTableItem>
</KeyTable>
